Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小女子不知世事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.45,0:00:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还请您多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.59,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.73,0:02:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.14,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.72,0:02:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一话  缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 已经这么晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的便当我很有信心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.52,0:03:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东京 东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请换乘JR各线路或地下铁各线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要搭哪辆车才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.01,0:04:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是樱花模样的花纹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么通不过剪票口呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鞋带…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋 该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能先扶着我的肩膀一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.89,0:05:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.03,0:05:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个都市里穿棉绸和服的还真少见呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰带的花纹有春天的感觉也很不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您很了解和服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微懂一点而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.59,0:05:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这只是应急一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是要拿去修理一下比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你对我这么亲切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.91,0:05:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是北上的车票吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 剪票口在那一边喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么怎么走才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.48,0:05:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这里一直往前走到了尽头后左转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在第一个楼梯口往右…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.53,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我想大概…没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.76,0:06:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直往前…一直往前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看样子会迷路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话 我现在正要回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车子刚好是同一条线 要不要一起走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还帮我把鞋带修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这份恩情我一辈子也不会忘记的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太夸张了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在东京车站换车 应该很困难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.12,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全搞不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在刚开始上大学的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也常常迷路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是大学生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今年春天之后就是三年级了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手好巧喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.97,0:06:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是指鞋带吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也很了解和服的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.51,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我小时候常穿和服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我母亲也常常穿棉绸和服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以跟你说话时没有那种陌生人的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然太多话了吧 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事 您帮了我大忙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.49,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对东京完全不了解 心里很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.73,0:07:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到喜欢和服的人不知怎么的就觉得很安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,户山台 户山台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有快车通过 请在此稍后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于坐到位子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一…二…三…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有四站就到泉之丘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是第一次来东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但又不像是来观光的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是为了找男朋友？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸上有什么东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以问一个问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到东京来干什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实…是为了和一个人见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是你的男朋友？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来只是打算开个玩笑的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚到底能不能见到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样子跑了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.66,0:08:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且路也完全不熟 真的非常的不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.86,0:08:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以很感谢您为我带路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很少一个人出远门…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么…有点想睡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.54,0:08:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泉之丘 泉之丘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.78,0:08:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是泉之丘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.05,0:08:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.12,0:08:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车开了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这该说是单纯好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是不知世事呢？真是可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.74,0:09:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.08,0:09:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就…还有多久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.92,0:09:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差点睡过头了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实已经走了一圈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.59,0:09:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是麻烦您照顾了 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.93,0:09:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西泉街吧 我也住在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.40,0:09:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个要去见的人是什么样的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.94,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经很久没有见面了 是个很温柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一想起那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会有种很安心的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.29,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起了小时候也发生过同样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也像今天一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.89,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鞋带断了 然后那个人帮我修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.13,0:10:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在想想 那个人手也很巧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么喜欢那个人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他是我有生以来第一个喜欢的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.68,0:10:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要想到那个人就觉得诞生在这个世上真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.25,0:10:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起 这么死心塌地的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能快点见到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纸条上写的 应该就是在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.47,0:10:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要转过这个弯就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在前面 那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.96,0:11:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走错了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 纸条写的的确是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.54,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.74,0:11:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还以为终于 终于能够见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.42,0:11:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝这个冷静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然请她到家里来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.99,0:12:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下该说些什么才好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.86,0:12:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去这个女孩子太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想让他们见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问 有没有其他的线索？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.18,0:12:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和他的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.22,0:12:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是小时候的照片呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…是在哪里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…不就是我和小葵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.24,0:13:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我和小葵的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是薰吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.75,0:13:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…我叫花菱薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.66,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.60,0:13:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.07,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十八年了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直一直在等这一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十八年？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样亲切地对我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然就是薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没有像此时此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此强烈感受到命运的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.92,0:13:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷…冷静一下 好好的说明一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.46,0:13:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫樱庭葵 是前来当薰的妻子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？妻子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.67,0:14:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我要成为薰的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的确是想起了你的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是小葵是我的妻子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.81,0:14:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持续了十八年的梦想终于实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 和我一起回到花菱家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花菱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.83,0:14:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到花菱家 我们两个就能在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要我回花菱家的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接来跟我说不就行了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然派这样的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.48,0:14:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用美人计来引诱我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更不相信花菱家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰…薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 我不会回花菱家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请你立刻给我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.30,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因为讨厌我才离开花菱家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差点就被骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是花菱家的那群人设计的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道计划失败了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有人来接她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.19,0:15:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 跟我想的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是花菱家的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐一个人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去卡拉OK啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在这种地方会感冒的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是要一起去找乐子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.75,0:15:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道个好地方哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.78,0:15:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个臭小子想干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是你打算出来跟我们抢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.99,0:16:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我们先找上的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有话就快说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说是挺身而出了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们看起来好像很厉害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.51,0:16:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的女人 你们有意见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.42,0:16:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕…我说出了什么不得了的话吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 有男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.06,0:16:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让一个女孩子在这种地方等你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.53,0:16:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.88,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…就算是说谎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被说是薰的女人 我实在太高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.39,0:17:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的好女孩怎么可能做那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.09,0:17:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我一时冲动误会你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之先回房间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去脚会痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.57,0:17:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.57,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,订婚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.91,0:17:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 小时候 见过好几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.80,0:17:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那个时候开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就为了成为薰的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了能照顾薰而被抚养长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.77,0:18:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰你不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.64,0:18:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好像有这么听说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上来讲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.08,0:18:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来就突然说要取消这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就想直接和薰见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问问你真正的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.23,0:18:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以到这里来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是因为讨厌你才离开花菱家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 有很多原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累了吧 今天就好好休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我可以待在这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.48,0:18:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都这么晚了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在去准备洗澡水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.32,0:18:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你有先征得家里人的同意才出来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用联络也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就先去洗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吧 好好泡一下暖暖身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的房间里竟然会有女孩子在洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.91,0:19:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连女孩子进来都还是第一次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.86,0:19:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇…脱和服的声音怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来这么诱人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.89,0:19:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十八年啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没听过这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋 她是个很好的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有不好的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.90,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是太突然了 实在是没办法接受…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.63,0:20:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
